## Q6 — Best mw-backend blueprint to clone

**`art_store_blueprint.py` is the cleanest template** (e-commerce pattern, in-memory store, JWT auth, no external deps, well-structured).

Blueprint scaffold to copy:
```python
from flask import Blueprint, request, jsonify
bowling_bp = Blueprint("bowling", __name__, url_prefix="/bowling")
# ... endpoints ...
```

Registration line in `server.py` (add after the last `register_blueprint` block, currently line ~358):
```python
from bowling_blueprint import bowling_bp
app.register_blueprint(bowling_bp)
```

Pattern: same as every other blueprint in the file — 2 lines, no special flags needed. CORS handled globally by server.py; no per-blueprint CORS config required.

