- decisions: Q1 = procedural mesh (no GLTF dependency risk); Q2 = canvas-generated patterns (no CDN dependency); Q5 = PHP is real, not narrative — winget check is the single gatekeeper, Flask-only fallback if unavailable; Q7 = drei Decal is confirmed technique.
